OL,3,CPolice in protective clothing respond
OL,4,Cto incident near Israeli embassy
OL,6,FPolice are investigating whether items
OL,7,Ffound near the Israeli embassy in
OL,8,Fcentral London are linked to a video
OL,9,Fwhich was posted online claiming it
OL,10,Fwas going to be attacked.
OL,12,FThe Metropolitan Police said there was
OL,13,Fan increased police presence in
OL,14,FKensington Gardens as officers in
OL,15,Fprotective clothing investigated a
OL,16,Fnumber of discarded items and have
OL,17,Furged people to avoid the area while
OL,18,Fthey carry out their work.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
