OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776427867
OL,3,CPolice in protective clothing respond
OL,4,Cto incident near Israeli embassy
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We do not
OL,7,Fbelieve there to be any increased
OL,8,Fpublic safety risk at this stage, but
OL,9,Fwe would urge people to avoid the area
OL,10,Fwhile officers carry out their work."
OL,12,FA cordon has been set up and access to
OL,13,Fthe gardens and the surrounding area
OL,14,Fhas been restricted.Police vans and a
OL,15,Fwhite tent can be seen at scene.
