OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776427867
OL,3,CPolice in protective clothing respond
OL,4,Cto incident near Israeli embassy
OL,6,FScotland Yard said Counter Terrorism
OL,7,FPolicing London was aware of a video
OL,8,Fshared online overnight, in which a
OL,9,Fgroup claim to have targeted the
OL,10,Fnearby Israeli embassy with drones
OL,11,Fcarrying dangerous substances.
OL,13,FPolice said the embassy had not been
OL,14,Fattacked, but said detectives were
OL,15,Fcarrying out enquiries to determine
OL,16,Fthe authenticity of the video and to
OL,17,Fidentify any potential link between it
OL,18,Fand the items discarded in Kensington
OL,19,FGardens.
